    "We use the official test set for the intra-category multi-tool instruction subset from ToolBench.",
    "The test set consists of 100 tasks.",
    "We build test instructions using the same approach as building multigranularity instructions in the training dataset.",
    "Specifically, we set the original test instructions at the hybrid level, and used these instructions, their corresponding tag lists, and instruction generation prompts to feed into the GPT-4 model to generate test instructions at the other three levels.",
